title: Second Blog Post
description:
This second post contains a single plot of the cars dataset.
It shows the relationship between the variables wt and mpg.
Not very exciting, but a start.
contents: This is a second post. Below is a bivariate scatterplot of the cars dataset showing the relationship between weight (wt) and miles per gallon (mpg). A modest start, but something to consider.
